frozen.name: ocaml4.12.0-menhirSdk
frozen.shortDescription: Compile-time library for auxiliary tools related to Menhir
frozen.longDescription:
Menhir is a LR(1) parser generator for the Objective Caml programming
language.  That is, Menhir compiles LR(1) grammar specifications down
to OCaml code.  Menhir was designed and implemented by François Pottier
and Yann Régis-Gianas.
